{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:24:32.952870+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me summarize my findings and provide the recommendation.\n\n## Summary of PR #1\n\nPR #1 (\"Add Finnish (fi) locale placeholder\") is a minimal marker PR. It adds a single HTML comment `<!-- host-pr marker: cs552 locale add baseline -->` to the bottom of `README.md`. It serves as the baseline commit for the locale extension workflow.\n\n## Current i18n Structure\n\nThe `core/lib/src/i18n/` directory currently contains:\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `inkino_en.arb` | English (en) ARB resource file |\n| `inkino_fi.arb` | Finnish (fi) ARB resource file (the template) |\n| `inkino_messages_en.dart` | Generated Dart delegate for English |\n| `inkino_messages_fi.dart` | Generated Dart delegate for Finnish |\n| `inkino_messages_all.dart` | Registry listing all locale delegates |\n| `messages.dart` | Base `AppMessages` class for the locale system |\n\n## Recommendation — Files to Touch for German (de) Support\n\nTo add German support following the established Finnish pattern, **six files** need to be touched:\n\n1. **`core/lib/src/i18n/inkino_de.arb`** *(create)* — The German ARB resource file, translated from `inkino_fi.arb`. Each key (e.g. `nowInTheaters`, `showtimes`, `tickets`, etc.) needs its German translation value.\n\n2. **`core/lib/src/i18n/inkino_messages_de.dart`** *(create)* — A new generated Dart file (modeled on `inkino_messages_fi.dart`) that imports the generated message lookup and provides the concrete `AppMessages` implementation for `de`.\n\n3. **`core/lib/src/i18n/inkino_messages_all.dart`** *(update)* — Add an import and map entry for `inkino_messages_de.dart` so the locale resolution system knows `de` is available.\n\n4. **`core/lib/src/i18n/messages.dart`** *(update)* — Register the German locale code in the supported-locales list / factory so the app can resolve `de` at runtime.\n\n5. **`mobile/pubspec.yaml`** *(update)* — If the project uses `intl_utils` or code-generation tooling driven by `pubspec.yaml` locale lists, add `'de'` to the supported locales. (Currently this file has no explicit locale list, but it depends on `intl` and `flutter_localizations`, so it may need a locale declaration depending on the build tooling.)\n\n6. **`README.md`** or a follow-up on PR #1 *(update)* — Optionally extend the host marker comment in PR #1 to reference the German locale addition, keeping the locale extension chain traceable.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 961, "prompt_tokens": 11457, "total_tokens": 12418, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 360, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8384, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0022030074, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0013669374, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00083607}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863852-BsV8C5bV1djIZngNGnLn", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c1-e007-7771-856b-d04f4f9055f4-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11457, "output_tokens": 961, "total_tokens": 12418, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8384}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 360}}}}]}}}
